聲，搞拌聲，切野聲之類"},{"pid":"895fb36ef284fa30c6ebb5a285c33930bcb82a18","tid":2071252,"uid":276969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b1adb7e184a3f3280bd4b9874bcde4ad9127af1","tid":2071252,"uid":275161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"片頭加個材料list<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nadd oil"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"好提議, 謝謝。"},{"pid":"ccea6080d99c7591ac9012b3364c3835469c6796","tid":2071252,"uid":276969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0de0280b045be2b562d803bdd08bbe639f7632d","tid":2071252,"uid":28588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:02:53.000Z","msg":"字型：黑體<br />\n字顏色：白色 / 白底黑字<br />\nD字大返小小，太多行數有時好難睇，可能分開上會好d<br />\n<br />\n可以某d鏡頭加返d環境音：倒野聲，搞拌聲，切野聲之類"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"環境聲好難, 屋企太多雜聲~<br />\n字型我改左了, 新片剪好我上來分享, 大家再指點下。"},{"pid":"0faf28539346782f18f18b25b82bd4a7182ca3fd","tid":2071252,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e6e9e3984d6c3d53d096ce388a30f3e850797b2","tid":2071252,"uid":276969,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fe514aac656988a7a91842dc6a082563634be3a7","tid":2071252,"uid":326032,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T16:29:31.000Z","msg":"換字體啦，唔想諗楝咩，就用黑體。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">（新細明體）這種字體我們稱為「內文」字體。通常，內文字會設計得讓人感覺變化不大，沒有張狂的造型，像喝水、呼吸那樣素然無味。但這樣「無聊」的體驗，反而有助於我們專心吸收資訊，而不太在意文字有什麼美感。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/新細明體就是醜-從桃園機場指標談用字型的設計思考/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E6%96%B0%E7%B4%B0%E6%98%8E%E9%AB%94%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E9%86%9C-%E5%BE%9E%E6%A1%83%E5%9C%92%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%E8%AB%87%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a46013cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E6%96%B0%E7%B4%B0%E6%98%8E%E9%AB%94%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E9%86%9C-%E5%BE%9E%E6%A1%83%E5%9C%92%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%E8%AB%87%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%2F&h=847fbc68\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/新細明體就是醜-從桃園機場指標談用字型的設計思考/</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"謝謝, 我下次拍改用黑體試試。<br />\n係唔係有人講野做旁白會好D?<br />\n呢段最新既會唔會好少少?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fIUYi67VIB0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfIUYi67VIB0&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=16183018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fIUYi67VIB0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T20:24:40.000Z","msg":"如果有懶音嘅話<br />\n唔出聲好過出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n芒果段片字體試用第隻色<br />\n背景光猛 用粉紅字體 撞哂<br />\n好難睇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>好似黑色mode用藍字咁撚樣</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有一開頭切完糯米糍<br />\n搵刀/餐具撥開<br />\n唔好搵手指<br />\n你咁樣撩開<br />\n好似撩鼻屎/劏緊唔知咩嘢咁<br />\n挖佢出嚟 好核突"},{"pid":"ffe2e738421503ca15fef2c318cc6580aab6e9a4","tid":2071252,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T20:37:24.000Z","msg":"仲有香港係用&quot;多士&quot;<br />\n唔係吐司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋樓主 bgm唔同人唔同口味<br />\n好似有人用恐怖音樂教整嘢食<br />\n鍾意獵奇嘢就會覺啱睇<br />\n但有啲人又會覺得恐怖"},{"pid":"0894788839772e693332f4a816eecd5e406cd0fa","tid":2071252,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T20:39:48.000Z","msg":"呢條片字體都ok<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dMf_IRJcfOI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdMf_IRJcfOI&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a7d89e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dMf_IRJcfOI</a>"},{"pid":"2c69bfbc7c8fa17ba7e6c994c3a0aefb673700ca","tid":2071252,"uid":82268,"like